HEADWORD: Earthling
<hw>Earth"ling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Earth</ets> +
<ets>-ling</ets>.]</ety> <def>An inhabitant of the earth; a
mortal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Earthlings</qex> oft her deemed a deity.</q>
<rj><qau>Drummond.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

